{"tha-ap508:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap508:0.2":"Kanikaravagga ","tha-ap508:0.3":"Matulungaphaladayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap508:1.1":"“Kanikaramva jalitam, ","tha-ap508:1.2":"punnamayeva candimam; ","tha-ap508:1.3":"Jalantam diparukkhamva, ","tha-ap508:1.4":"addasam lokanayakam. ","tha-ap508:2.1":"Matulungaphalam gayha, ","tha-ap508:2.2":"adasim satthuno aham; ","tha-ap508:2.3":"Dakkhineyyassa virassa, ","tha-ap508:2.4":"pasanno sehi panibhi. ","tha-ap508:3.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap508:3.2":"yam phalam adadim tada; ","tha-ap508:3.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap508:3.4":"phaladanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap508:4.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap508:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap508:4.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap508:5.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap508:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap508:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap508:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap508:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap508:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap508:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma matulungaphaladayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap508:8.1":"Matulungaphaladayakattherassapadanam chattham. "}